stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Idle
    Idle --> RequestPIN : User initiates login
    RequestPIN --> EnterPIN : Prompt for PIN
    EnterPIN --> VerifyPIN : User enters PIN
    VerifyPIN --> Success : PIN is correct
    VerifyPIN --> Failure : PIN is incorrect
    Failure --> EnterPIN : Retry entering PIN
    Success --> [*] : Login successful
    Idle --> [*] : No action taken